item.title: Anatomy of a page
item.description: Home Section Subsection Content page Anatomy of a page Lead paragraph (p class=”lead”). This page aims to show the basic building blocks of a page build using the Dewey design system. While different layouts will vary from this formula, this structure should be used as a starting point and altered to suit a website’s specific purpose. This example shows both page content here on the left and a right hand navigation.
